{"lemma":"شَفا","slug":"شَفا","root":"ش.ف.#","root_slug":"ش-ف-_","root_link":"/words/roots/ش-ف-_","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"شَفا","root":"شفو","pos":"N","occurrence_count":2},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":3},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n22681"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B4%D9%8E%D9%81%D8%A7"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to near setting (said of the Sun)"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to appear, to nigh"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"extremity, verge, brink, edge"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"From شَفَة (šafa, “lip; brink, border”)."},"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n22681","headword_ar":"شَفًا","root":"$fw and $fY","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"point"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"extremity, verge, brink,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"edge,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of anything; (S, Msb, K, &c.;) like ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$afapN","text_ar":"شَفَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$afaA AlHuforapi","text_ar":"شَفَا الحُفْرَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ksh in iii. 99) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$afaA Albiy^ori","text_ar":"شَفَا البِيْرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Bd ibid.) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$afatuhaA","text_ar":"شَفَتُهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"both signify the same, (Ksh, Bd,) i. e."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HarofuhaA","text_ar":"حَرْفُهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ksh) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TarafuhaA","text_ar":"طَرَفُهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Bd;) but the final"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"w","text_ar":"و"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the former is changed into"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A","text_ar":"ا"},{"kind":"text","text":", and in the latter [accord. to those who hold"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$afapN","text_ar":"شَفَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"to be originally"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$afowapN","text_ar":"شَفْوَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"] it is elided; (Ksh, Bd;)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$afFA","text_ar":"شَفًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"being originally"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$afawN","text_ar":"شَفَوٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Bd:) [but"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$afFA","text_ar":"شَفًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"generally signifies as expl. above; and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$afapN","text_ar":"شَفَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"almost always signifies the “ lip ” of a human being:] the dual is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$afawaAni","text_ar":"شَفَوَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; this being known, as Akh says, by the fact that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_imaAlap","text_ar":"اـِمَالَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the word"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$afFA","text_ar":"شَفًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"is not allowable: (S:) and the pl. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^a$ofaA='N","text_ar":"اَشْفَا=ءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) It is said in the Kur [iii. 99],"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wakunotumo EalaY $afaA HuforapN mina A@ln~aAri faA^anoqa*akumo minohaA","text_ar":"وَكُنْتُمْ عَلَى شَفَا حُفْرَةٌ مِنَ ا@لنَّارِ فَاَنْقَذَكُمْ مِنْهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And ye were on the verge,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"brink, of a pit of the fire"},{"kind":"text","text":"of Hell,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and He saved,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rescued, you from it"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S.) And one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa EalaY $afaA AlhalaAki","text_ar":"هُوَ عَلَى شَفَا الهَلَاكِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He is on the brink of destruction"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) ―         -b2-  Also (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A little;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, K, TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a small part,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"portion; somewhat;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"somewhat remaining"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the moon when near the change, (K, TA, ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlhalAk","text_ar":"الهَلاك"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the CK is erroneously put for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlhilaAl","text_ar":"الهِلَال"},{"kind":"text","text":",]) and of the sight ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlbaSar","text_ar":"البَصَر"},{"kind":"text","text":"), and of the day, and the like, as in the T. (TA.) One says of a man on the occasion of his dying, and of the moon at [the last period of the month called] its"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muHaAq","text_ar":"مُحَاق"},{"kind":"text","text":", and of the sun at its setting, (S,)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA baqiYa minohu A_il~aA $afFA","text_ar":"مَا بَقِىَ مِنْهُ اـِلَّا شَفًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"[and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"minohaA","text_ar":"مِنْهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"when said of the sun] (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"There has not remained of him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it, save a little:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K: *) and [in like manner]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mina AlEumuri","text_ar":"مِنَ العُمُرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of life"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S.) And one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^atayotuhu","text_ar":"اَتَيْتُهُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bi$afFA mino Dawo'i Al$~amosi","text_ar":"بِشَفًا مِنْ ضَوْءِ الشَّمْسِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I came to him in a time when there was little remaining of the light of the sun"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) El-'Ajjáj says,"},{"kind":"quote","text":"A^a$orafotuhu bilaA $afFA A^awo bi$afaA \n                      \n                     \n                        wamirobaA^K EaAlK limanN ta$ar~afaA"},{"kind":"text","text":"meaning ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Many an elevated place of observation, high to him who ascends"},{"kind":"text","text":"it,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I have ascended"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"when the sun had set or when there was somewhat of it remaining."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.) One says also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaAra fiY $afaA","text_ar":"صَارَ فِى شَفَا"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alqamari","text_ar":"القَمَرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"meaning (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, in the last part of the night."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And it is said in a trad., (in relation to [the temporary marriage termed]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlmutoEap","text_ar":"المُتْعَة"},{"kind":"text","text":",)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"falawo laA nahoyuhu EanohaA maA A@HotaAja A_ilaY Alz~inaA A_il~aA $afFA","text_ar":"فَلَوْ لَا نَهْيُهُ عَنْهَا مَا ا@حْتَاجَ اـِلَى الزِّنَا اـِلَّا شَفًا"},{"kind":"text","text":", accord. to the T meaning ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Were it not for his"},{"kind":"text","text":"(i. e. God's)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"forbidding it, none would need having recourse to fornication,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"save a small number of men:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, TA:) or, accord. to 'Atà, it means,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"but would be on the brink thereof, without falling into it;"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$afFA","text_ar":"شَفًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"being thus used in the place of the inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_i$ofaA='","text_ar":"اـِشْفَا=ء"},{"kind":"text","text":": so says IAth, as from Az. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["Ksh","Bd","S","T","TA"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}